Python -M Venv Venv
来源VENV/bin/activate
pip安装carconnectivity-connector-volkswagen == 0.5a1 carconnnectivity-plugin-mqtt carconnectivity-plugin-mqtt_homeassistant
vim carconnectivity.json  
